(482, 1, '2019-08-26 00:52:42', '2019-08-25 21:52:42', '', 'Adidas Performance Performance Ultraboost 19 M', '<strong>Ultraboost</strong> reinvented. These running shoes reboot key performance technologies to give you a confident and energy-filled run. The knit upper has a second-skin fit and is built with motion-weave technology for adaptive stretch and support. Dual-density cushioning delivers medial support and an energized ride.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Regular fit</li>\r\n 	<li>Lace closure</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>adidas Primeknit 360</strong> upper</li>\r\n 	<li>Synthetic lining</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Stretchweb</strong> outsole flexes naturally for an energized ride, and <strong>Continental</strong>™ <strong>Rubber</strong>gives you superior traction</li>\r\n 	<li>Dual-density <strong>Boost</strong> cushioning under arch</li>\r\n 	<li>Natural feel like a second skin</li>\r\n 	<li>Weight: 11 ounces (size 9)</li>\r\n 	<li>Midsole drop: 10 mm (heel: 29 mm / forefoot: 19 mm)</li>\r\n 	<li>Arch type: Normal</li>\r\n 	<li>Lightweight 3D heel frame for personalized fit</li>\r\n 	<li>Stabilizing Torsion Spring</li>\r\n</ul>', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'adidas-performance-performance-ultraboost-19-m', '', '', '2019-08-26 01:49:05', '2019-08-25 22:49:05', '', 0, 'http://localhost/eshop/?post_type=product&#038;p=482', 0, 'product', '', 0),
